      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个应用启动流程图，核心是从App Launch开始，经过一系列检查点，最后到达主界面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App Launch",
        "User proceeds to main UI"
