      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是App Launch，终点是用户进入主界面。中间这些检查点是什么类型的？判断节点还是处理步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App Launch",
        "User proceeds to main UI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第一步应该是加载配置和状态，然后第一个分叉是判断是否离线。离线的话要走C1分支，显示离线提示并限制功能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Load config + state",
        "Offline?",
        "C1",
        "limited actions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把起始部分画出来：App Launch → 加载配置和状态 → 离线判断节点。C1我标记为显示离线通知、功能受限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App Launch",
        "Load config + state",
        "Offline?",
        "C1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果不在线，C1处理完后不能直接进主界面，要等所有弹窗检查走完。我们先继续主线：不在线的话，下一个检查是是否有待处理的重启需求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Offline?",
        "C1",
        "Pending restart required?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Offline判断为No时走到Pending restart，那如果用户选择稍后重启，这个D1节点怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Offline?",
        "Pending restart required?",
        "D1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "D1要给用户两个选择：立即重启或者 postpone 延后处理。无论选哪个，最后都要汇合到统一出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "Prompt restart or postpone",
        "postp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "D1画好了，标记为Prompt restart or postpone。继续往下，No分支走到E节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D1",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
